block body
    .starter-template
        .container
            .page-header
                h1 About Us 
                    small STEM Students
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                p.
                    We&rsquo;re a small group of technology-focused, forward-looking individuals
                    dedicated to the improvement of our STEM-oriented school and of the STEM
                    community as a whole.
                .list-group
                    +bio("Andrew Chronister", "https://github.com/chronister/", "http://twitter.com/p0rtalplayer").
