                        technologies and presiding over the school&rsquo;s Programming Club. 
                    +bio("Mrigank Bhardwaj", "https://github.com/mikkuthebhard/").
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet etc etc placeholder text and such to fill
                        the space left in this gap. Biographies are neat and interesting too.
                    +bio("Jay Tayade", "https://github.com/jaytayade").
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet etc etc placeholder text and such to fill
